 Track: &quot;Chaos&quot;<P>

 Walking,Breathing,
 Our hidden Fireside Place,
 In the morning Sun we`re leaving.
 Walkin`,Jokin`,
 It seems that all is right,
 Until we reach our Home this Night.<P>

