 Track: &quot;A Friend has Died&quot;<P>

 Kneeling before him,
 All over the slim,
 Watching him die,
 Blood on my feet.<P>

 &quot;I`ve done my best&quot;, he said,
 &quot;Now it`s your Turn...&quot;.<P>

 Refrain 1:
 ------------------------------------------------
 Old Friend of mine:
 Don`t die on me,it`s all my Fault,
 I wasn`t here for your support.
 Don`t die on me,my Hero you are,
 to the Gods Altar ? Then you are so far...
 ------------------------------------------------<P>

 &quot;Pal,the Time to fight has come,
  take my Sword,you`re the chosen One.
  My Time`s Up,Time to make a cut,
  hold our Banner high,faithfull in our Sky !&quot;<P>

 Refrain 2:
 ----------------------------------------------------
 Old Friend of mine:
 Don`t die on me,it`s all my Fault,
 I wasn`t here for your support.
 Don`t die on me,I`m not the chosen One,
 This Sword is yours,your Time hasn`t come...
 ----------------------------------------------------<P>

 Kneeling before him,
 I started to cry.
 Watching my old Friend,
 watching him die.<P>

 &quot;The Sky is black,This Place is doomed,
  but in my Hand,Our Glory couldn`t bloomed.
  Now heed the Call,Thy shall be done,
  I`m leaving now,my Time has come...&quot;<P>

 Kneeling before him,
 I started screaming.
 My Hero,My Pal,
 he`s gone,he`s leaving.<P>

 Refrain 3:
 ------------------------------------------------
 Old Friend of mine:
 You died on me and it`s all my Fault,
 I wasn`t here for any support.
 I swear Revenge,whatever it cost,
 even then if life will be lost...
 ------------------------------------------------<P>
