 Track: &quot;Stranger&quot;<P>
<P>

 It`s been a long Time ago,
 We`ve joined up this Town.
 I remember that punch,Pain of a Clown,
 as we were there,with Stones we were thrown.<P>

 Yeah,we are Strangers,but that doesn`t matter,
 what do you think we`re trying to do ?
 Hiding and making Terror 2 b cool ?
 Don`t be a Fool,we`re almost like you !<P>

 No one trust me, &quot;You !&quot;, they said,
 &quot;A Stranger ? Here`s no place for you !&quot;.
 Also my Father,he came with me through,
 also a Stranger,but Humans like you !<P>

 Then I met him on the Streets of the Market,
 A young Warrior of Pride.
 From the beginning he was a Friend of mine,
 always travelling side by side.<P>

