 Track: &quot;Metal for Revenge&quot;<P>
<P>

 The Pain inside,it`s coming outside,
 We still remember the Battle We`ve lost.
 Our Bodies defeated,But our Soul still lives on,
 watch out you Bastards,you haven`t won !
 A Thorn in our side,this mighty Pain,
 Defeaten by an unholy Rain ?
 No,It can`t be `cause all that we`ve gain:
 Ouself, Our Soul will remain the same...<P>

 Refrain:
 ---------------------------------------------
 Metal:    For Revenge !
 Revenge:  The Warlord cries !
 Cries:    They will not hear !
 Hear:     Hypochondria appear !
 ---------------------------------------------<P>

 Metal in our Temple,for the Throne of Bones,
 we`re playing and watching them die.
 Damn on you Bastards,you`re so foolish too,
 Our Time has come,reaching out for you.
 Our Sound of Thunder just make you cry,
 Swimming against the River and will die !
 Bring the Guitar and we`ll finally end,
 Bring the whole World under Metal`s command.<P>

